MASM program which:
 - displays name and program title
 - gets user name and greets user
 - displays user instructions
 - repeatedly prompts user for number 
 - validates user input [-100, -1]
 - counts and accumulates the user numbers until a non-negative number is entered (non-negative is discarded)
 - calculates the (rounded int) average of the negative numbers
 - displays number of negative numbers entered 
 - displays sum and average of negative numbers
 - displays terminating message